data.title: Iqra-Prospectus Complete PDF
data.meta_description: Iqra-Prospectus_Complete.pdf - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document is a prospectus for Iqra University's Islamabad campus that provides an overview of the university. It begins with a message from the Chairman welcoming new students and outlining the benefits of studying at Iqra University. It then provides information on the university's mission, facilities, academic programs, policies, and departments. Key facilities highlighted include qualified faculty, libraries, computer labs, sports facilities, and a cafeteria. The prospectus aims to provide prospective students with information on resources and opportunities available at Iqra University's Islamabad campus.
